        <p class="text-primary/70 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-xl">
          At Lumière Studio, we believe hair is the ultimate canvas. Our philosophy blends timeless elegance with modern innovation, creating bespoke looks that reflect your unique essence. 
        </p>
        <p class="text-primary/70 leading-relaxed text-lg max-w-xl">
          From the moment you step into our minimalist sanctuary, every detail is curated for your comfort and transformation. We don't just style hair; we craft confidence.
